{"tid":1797190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角青年墮樓案　警方表示傷者自稱醉酒仆傷 改列有人意外受傷處理。","createTime":"2019-12-25T08:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T08:46:10.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cfdd0e4c9484a7cfe423bca01036de66d65eb42d","tid":1797190,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374526&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=076d7624\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374526&h=0a6de64e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374526</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】旺角凌晨持續衝突期間，一名青年懷疑被追捕時從高處墮樓。警方其後表示，傷者因醉酒仆倒受傷，改列有人意外受傷處理。<br />\n<br />\n16歲傷者手腳跌傷，被送到伊利沙伯醫院時清醒。他的親友接獲通知到醫院陪伴及了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，在醫院向傷者調查後，有人聲稱曾經飲酒，懷疑受酒精影響下仆倒受傷。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨約二時三十分，一批防暴警員在旺角一帶驅逐聚集市民時，傳出有人在長沙街與砵蘭街交界一幢大廈從高處墮樓跌落一處草叢，警方到場處理期間引來大批市民圍觀。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，警方一度舉旗警告，並向圍觀人士射胡椒噴霧，有兩個人受傷。另外兩名男子懷疑鬧事，被警方制服帶走。當警方準備離開時，突然有警員從車上擲出一個催淚彈驅散市民。<br />\n<br />\n事件持續至清晨五時許，警方清理彌敦道路障後撤離，市民亦陸續散去。"},{"pid":"9a52cd4ce91f783b5523f6441a42dfe5d44d96f8","tid":1797190,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef2baa6b53791f285f49485b020cb9d4215a545","tid":1797190,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3cde89963c7615a191988699808d488eca3b1c","tid":1797190,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edebca5f0b4bcceb70544613200f28f6aacecd2","tid":1797190,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"私人檢控"},{"pid":"dd76da11d38b47d6aebf8947f1d3fafbe1c478ac","tid":1797190,"uid":107414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"16歲可以飲酒？"},{"pid":"c5a15ffd1571f2c95ac77c00b8ab4f7da880088d","tid":1797190,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:34:14.000Z","msg":"依家真係連文宣都要開花, 靠區議員就大鑊啦! 仲要等出年?<br />\n<br />\n[行動]唔好以為過咗1月1號就周圍都有連儂牆&mdash;文宣都要開花! A4 size label 周圍貼! (更新)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1797038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1797038</a>"},{"pid":"ee3ae0e91351c0b564782e7c2f9b11cd7bf4ea42","tid":1797190,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7AgFfC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7AgFfC.png&h=4406e579&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"123fdbc4a470a47107476b4bbd84d4e9b37e41cf","tid":1797190,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a90692f1cf9551907254940211b59eb83b4f8b9","tid":1797190,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:42:32.000Z","msg":"被醉酒"},{"pid":"19dd1ada14257f15f2b1f00e566664edd7037168","tid":17